yTime":"2017-08-19T03:48:00.000Z","msg":"脫咗兩年幾，每個月脫一次，成功脫到可以一日一次<br />\n剃鬚每次一刀就乾淨晒<br />\n之前如果出街要到11、12點一定要下午剃一次夜晚再剃一次先乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係旺角做，6000蚊做15次包埋麻藥，facial 嗰啲，又會慢慢做，做幾個鐘都唔會發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身啲鬚勁到打一下都會痛到喊，冇麻藥/慢慢做我真係會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預計脫多一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36d750d5879fa12936ca690de35319313b4b4fa","tid":364363,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"韓國支那文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797a0c8116568da7edf210d26c424f3c8aad3c03","tid":364363,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"幾時脫哂d毛？仲係男人咩"},{"pid":"36eeaaf53e6a3838f1b8d61a37b21a4615944242","tid":364363,"uid":22663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留鬚咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔啱我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望落好唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如剃個光頭，咁咪好乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5930d40cb94175b1af5d8e905db969dd6dc61b4f","tid":364363,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T03:55:46.000Z","msg":"塊面cheeks做左，會好痛，下巴冇做因為太太太痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7d08efc874be405b34dd65c0f5bb8d31d2cfe0b","tid":364363,"uid":60563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾時脫哂d毛？仲係男人咩</blockquote><br />\n唔好再一廂情願覺得留鬚好撚man<img src=\"/assets/faces